uploads/getty_images/1642600704/image_1642600704.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1642600704/image_1642600704.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1642600704/image_1642600704.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1642600704/image_1642600704.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1642600704/image_1642600704.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1642600704/image_1642600704.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1642600704/image_1642600704.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The \"animal spirits\" that have driven the stock markets to all-time highs in the wake of Trump's reelection seems to be cooling off somewhat, and against this backdrop it's a great time for investors to be carefully pruning their portfolios. I'm especially</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1642600704/image_1642600704.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743531-yext-this-low-quality-software-business-is-overdue-for-a-pullback", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 15:03:06"}, {"id": "4743394", "title": "3 'Wide Moat' REITs (1 Is A Strong Buy)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/534921083/image_534921083.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medieval castle\" data-id=\"534921083\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" src